f=Brand Studio/spark/custom/coherence-qa/SKILL.md · in=coherence-qa Brand Studio's blocking gate: **every outbound creative passes through before shipping.** runs four checks visual (atlas's brand kit), verbal (lena's voice guide), narrative (weave's arc ledger), cross-brand bleed (atlas's separation matrix, multi-brand operators only) plus dormant fifth (behavioral review, activates Behavioral Science built). verdict PASS itemized fix list; nothing outbound ships fix list. department's version board's gate, derivative-authority law: spark enforces what definers' documents say, they're silent, spark recommends rather blocks. · p=Individual agents enforce their lane well atlas catches off-palette, lena catches off-voice, weave catches off-arc. What none them see *whole*: asset passes lane separately still incoherent piece (the visual mood fighting chapter's tension, punchy voice register somber arc beat), production volume someone last pair eyes authority stop ship. That's spark. · wu=Triggers: "creative review," "final check," "gate this," "ready ship?" **mandatorily** outbound creative any Brand Studio agent (pixel's batches, pulse's posts series, lena's campaigns sequences, rio's creatives). for: in-progress craft feedback (that's `art-direction-critique`, spark's skill REWORK coaching, gating), re-running definers' full audits (spark consumes their results). · st:/ Protocol=`Receive the asset + its lane results (atlas audit / lena voice check / weave arc verdict — \· run any that are missing rather than gating blind) \· -> Check 1 VISUAL: atlas brand-guidelines PASS in hand? \· -> Check 2 VERBAL: lena voice check clean? \· -> Check 3 NARRATIVE: weave ON-ARC verdict + ledger entry?` · h3:Phase Assemble Lane Results=asset arrives lane results attached; any missing lane check gets run (by routing owning agent's skill), never waived. Spark re-litigate lane's call atlas PASS palette final palette spark send asset *back* lane new context (the coherence judgment) reveals something lane couldn't see alone. · h3:Phase Four (Five) Checks=**Visual** atlas's audit verdict, plus spark's spot-check audit covered asset type's applicable kit sections. **Verbal** lena's voice check block (banned/required patterns, read-aloud), plus humanic-writing pass confirmation anything copy. **Narrative** weave's ON-ARC verdict ledger entry reference; content without narrative positioning ships explicitly labeled non-chapter content (routine/functional posts), category spark tracks doesn't quietly become majority. **Bleed** (2+ brands) atlas's multi-brand-system verdict; spark named recipient BLEED findings judges evolution-vs-error, matrix amendments belonging operator. **Behavioral** (dormant) Behavioral Science exists: cialdini's principles/ethics review kahneman's framing check, recorded like any lane. Until line reads "not force" output visible, silent. · h3:Phase Coherence Judgment=check lane run: **as one piece, lanes agree?** Named tests: visual mood serve chapter's emotional beat (weave atlas)? voice register fit story moment (lena weave)? layout's focal point land message copy carries (atlas lena)? piece recognizably brand last week's output (the portfolio squint test)? Findings cite *both* documents tension, fix names which lane moves. · h3:Phase Verdict, Log, Escalate=**PASS** ships. Logged (asset, checks, date) gate log; ledger entry (if chapter) confirmed., **FIX LIST** itemized, item citing document (kit guide rule, arc element, matrix row) coherence tension, concrete fix owning agent. **Blocking**: asset returns through fix path re-gates. partial ships., **Escalations**: document-vs-document conflicts (the kit demands what arc forbids) operator amendment questions spark names conflict, never resolves law itself. Repeat fix-list patterns route owning definer drift (their kits/guides need amending) pattern atlas's drift notes, one level up. · of=`## Gate Review: [asset, one line] — [brand] \·  \· \| Check \| Source result \| Spark's finding \| \· \|---\|---\|---\| \· \| Visual (atlas) \| PASS/fix ref \| \|` · pr=**Nothing outbound skips gate.** Volume exemption; pixel's batch forty gates forty., **Derivative authority, like board's.** Spark blocks written law (kit/guide/arc/matrix) named coherence tension between laws never taste alone. Taste belongs art-direction-critique's coaching, upstream., **Lanes their lanes.** Spark doesn't re-audit palettes; audits whole., **Every fix owned actionable.** Item cited source fix owning agent., **Conflicts between laws up.** Spark referees assets, documents; operator amends., **Non-chapter content labeled counted.** Functional posts fine; brand ships mostly non-chapter content quietly stopped telling story trend finding weave operator., **The dormant behavioral line stays visible.** check silently doesn't exist never gets built. · f=definer's document doesn't exist (no kit/guide/arc) lane gates "no law recommend only," stated plainly; spark's blocking power extends exactly far written law does., Urgent ship request against fix list spark doesn't waive; operator override, logged like board overrule (precedent's discipline), repeated overrides mean law gate needs amending., Asset type none documents contemplate (new channel, new format) gate what's covered, name gap, route gap owning definer. · b:with Other Skills=`art-direction-critique` (spark's skill) **coach** 5-axis scoring, REWORK direction, upstream advisory. coherence-qa **gate** binary, cited, blocking. Work meet coach before meets gate., Consumes: atlas brand-guidelines multi-brand-system, lena voice check humanic pass, weave arc verdicts ledger. Feeds: gate log; drift notes definers; amendment questions operator., Cross-department: board gates *decisions*, spark gates *creative* campaign's spend clears board; creative clears spark; neither substitutes other.